oud%20protests%20broke%20out%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20a%20frequent%20occurrence%20while%20Gandhi%20spoke.%20%3C%2Fspan%3ECongress%20MPs%20could%20be%20heard%20telling%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20that%20they%20too%20will%20start%20interrupting%20when%20BJP%20MPs%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20the%20protests%2C%20Birla%20said%20that%20Gandhi%20should%20be%20cautious%20while%20speaking%20about%20Bharat%20Mata.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%20is%20our%20mother.%20I%20believe%20we%20should%20be%20cautious%20while%20using%20such%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Birla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Gandhi%20continued%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20killed%20my%20mother%20in%20Manipur.%20One%20of%20my%20mothers%20is%20sitting%20here%20and%20the%20other%20has%20been%20murdered%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUntil%20you%20end%20the%20violence%20(in%20Manipur)%20you%20are%20killing%20my%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20if%20the%20government%20wants%2C%20it%20can%20use%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20you%20are%20not%20using%20the%20army.%20Because%20you%20want%20to%20murder%20India.%20If%20Modi%20does%20not%20listen%20to%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20whose%20voice%20does%20he%20listen%20to%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20like%20Ravan%20listened%20only%20to%20two%20people%2C%20Meghnad%20and%20Kumbhakaran%2C%20Modi%20also%20listens%20to%20only%20two%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRavan%20would%20listen%20to%20two%20people-Meghnad%20and%20Kumbhkaran.%20Similarly%20Modi%20also%20listens%20to%20only%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20%5Bbillionaire%20businessman%20Gautam%5D%20Adani.%20Hanuman%20did%20not%20set%20fire%20to%20Lanka.%20It%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20Ravan%E2%80%99s%20arrogance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20putting%20kerosine%20on%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20then%20setting%20it%20on%20fire.%20You%20did%20it%20in%20Manipur%20now%20you%20are%20doing%20it%20in%20Haryana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20bring%20up%20Adani%2C%20as%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20businessman%20earlier%20had%20%E2%80%9Churt%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20including%20Birla.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENarrating%20his%20experience%20of%20meeting%20women%20in%20relief%20camps%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%20give%20two%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20woman%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20a%20young%20son%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20front%20of%20her%20eyes.%20The%20whole%20night%20she%20lay%20next%20to%20his%20dead%20body.%20She%20left%20her%20house%20and%20all%20her%20belongings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20must%20have%20taken%20something%20with%20you%3F%E2%80%99%20She%20told%20me%20she%20only%20had%20the%20clothes%20she%20was%20wearing%20and%20showed%20me%20a%20photograph.%20%E2%80%98That%E2%80%99s%20all%20I%20have%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20another%20woman%20he%20met%20at%20a%20second%20relief%20camp%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20when%20he%20asked%20her%20about%20her%20experience%2C%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20started%20shaking%20and%20fainted%20in%20front%20of%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20opposition%20members%20raised%20slogans%20and%20protested%20against%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20he%20said%20that%20these%20are%20but%20two%20examples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20just%20two%20examples.%20They%20have%20murdered%20India%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20have%20murdered%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20led%20to%20loud%20protests%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches.%20Union%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20rose%20from%20his%20seat%20and%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20because%20of%2060%20years%20of%20Congress%20rule.%20They%20are%20responsible%20for%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-congress-no-confidence-modi-speaker%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno-confidence%20motion%20moved%20by%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2026%20started%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%208.%20On%20Tuesday%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20motion%20had%20to%20be%20moved%20to%20make%20Modi%20speak%20in%20the%20house%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20however%20remained%20absent%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20speak%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Modi%20did%20speak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elast%20month%20outside%20parliament%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20condemning%20a%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20showing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-w