pital%20city%20of%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20new%20and%20old%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20suffering%20because%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20naughty%20boy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20Kejriwal%20but%20the%20citizens%20who%20mindlessly%20keep%20electing%20him%20and%20his%20parvenu%20party%20are%20the%20disaffected%20naughty%20boy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%20there%20were%20the%20interminable%2015%20years%20of%20Sheila%20Dixit%20and%20the%20decrepit%20Congress%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fddnews.gov.in%2Fnational%2Farvind-kejriwal-sworn-chief-minister-delhi-third-time%5C%22%3Ethen%2010%20more%20of%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20so-called%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnbearably%20galling%20that%20a%20beloved%20Delhi%20in%20which%20the%20King%20hath%20his%20abode%20should%20be%20without%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20party%20in%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20here%20and%20there%2C%20but%20not%20where%20the%20seat%20is%20the%20most%20puissant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20that%20it%20was%20the%20late%20Madan%20Lal%20Khurana%20who%20first%20demanded%20full%20statehood%20for%20Delhi%3B%20and%20now%20to%20have%20Hastinapur%20ruled%20by%20a%20mere%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20nobody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20if%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20may%20override%20the%20centuries%20of%20Hindu%20sacredness%20that%20suffuses%20the%20ancient%20metropolis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20if%20the%20principle%20of%20representation%20means%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%2C%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20will%20turn%20their%20back%20on%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20party%20which%20alone%20holds%20the%20patent%20to%20that%20sacred%20trust%2C%20then%20clearly%2C%20the%20principle%20of%20representation%20must%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20this%20outdated%20principle%20has%20disappeared%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20crown%20of%20Brahminical%20knowledge%20that%20remained%20subjugated%20by%20forces%20inimical%20to%20that%20storehouse%20of%20%3Cem%3Egyan%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20blind-sided%20democrats%20will%20deny%20how%20that%20hitherto%20thwarted%20state%20has%20flourished%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20ways%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdilution-of-article-370-brought-unprecedented-progress-and-security-to-jk-centre-tells-sc%5C%22%3Etoo%20subtle%20to%20be%20enumerated%3C%2Fa%3E)%20since%20the%20eradication%20of%20the%20plebeian%20principle%20of%20representation%20in%20favour%20of%20rule%20by%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20enlightened%20emissary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20is%20simple%3A%20either%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20have%20the%20good%20sense%20and%20loyalty%20to%20elect%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20party%20everywhere%2C%20or%20else%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbasic%20structure%E2%80%9D%20(fah!)%20of%20representative%20governance%20must%20yield%20to%20the%20superior%20structure%20of%20a%20revived%20Princely%20arrangement%2C%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governors%20and%20Governors%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%20re-christened%20as%20Princes%20who%20must%20be%20understood%20to%20be%20imbued%20with%20the%20flawless%20virtues%20of%20the%20King%20who%2C%20like%20the%20Bard%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpast%2C%20present%2C%20and%20future%20sees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-