e%20fatal%20year%20of%202024%2C%20and%20the%20outdated%20constitution%20that%20makes%20such%20fetish%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20representation%20could%20be%20ready%20to%20be%20rearranged%2C%20following%20the%20example%20of%20the%20stout%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20making%20it%20lawful%20for%20the%20King%20to%20administer%20the%20realm%20till%20the%20expiry%20of%20his%20natural%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20promise%20of%20stability%20that%2C%20imagine%2C%20even%20if%20the%20republic%20may%20lose%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%E2%80%9D%20part%20and%20retain%20just%20the%20royal%20%E2%80%9Cre%E2%80%9D%20betokening%20%E2%80%9Cregality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThink%20that%20some%20other%20countries%20seem%20ahead%20in%20these%20advanced%20imaginings%2C%20while%20Bharat%20still%20lacks%20the%20courage%20of%20conviction%2C%20squeamishly%20still%20adhering%20to%20the%20electoral%20principle%2C%20even%20if%20only%20to%20consolidate%20monarchy%20rather%20sheepishly%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20there%20is%20the%20answer%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20problems%2C%20and%2C%20by%20extension%20to%20all%20those%20un-evolved%20parts%20of%20the%20republic%20which%20still%20choose%20to%20reject%20the%20munificence%20that%20issues%20from%20committing%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Celect%E2%80%9D%20only%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20then%20should%20a%20Delhi%20or%20a%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20recourse%20to%20a%20fruitless%20%E2%80%9Crepresentative%E2%80%9D%20assembly%20of%20spoilers%3F%20Or%20to%20self-important%20chief%20ministers%20who%20wish%20to%20put%20themselves%20above%20the%20superior%20mandate%20and%20all-knowing%20expertise%20of%20sundry%20bureaucrats%20and%20techno-savvy%20elites%20who%20alone%20can%20show%20the%20way%20to%20profit%20maximisation%20and%20the%20fearful%20force%20of%20centralised%20political%20gunpowder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20to%20educating%20our%20young%20and%20aspiring%20generations%20who%20would%20rather%20die%20for%20the%20nation%20than%20live%20for%20it%20sensibly%2C%20let%20it%20suffice%20to%20have%20them%20read%20the%20%3Cem%3ESaffron%20book%20of%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20emulating%20the%20prophetic%20examples%20of%20Mao%20Zedong%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERed%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EBook%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Muammar%20Gadaffi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EGreen%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ebook%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20indeed%20most%20heartening%20that%20such%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Fmann-ki-baat-motivational-tales-to-reach-students-in-comic-format-across-jk-schools%5C%22%3Eintended%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stroke%20of%20genius%20guaranteed%20to%20bring%20back%20to%20the%20straight%20and%20narrow%20all%20those%20whose%20impressionable%20minds%20wander%20into%20questioning%20pathways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20in%20a%20millennium%20has%20ever%20any%20part%20of%20the%20globe%20been%20blessed%20with%20a%20Kingship%20as%20everywhere%20and%20as%20ready-to-the-task%20as%20is%20Bharat%2C%20and%20as%20faultless%20in%20all%20matters%20that%20touch%20the%20lives%20of%20gawking%20hoi%20polloi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMake%20the%20best%20use%20of%20that%20good%20fortune%20and%20stop%20fretting%20about%20the%20disappearance%20of%20the%20representative%20principle%2C%20and%20about%20the%20constitutional%20rights%20of%20elected%20assemblies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20many%20have%20a%20King%20who%20is%20omnipresent%2C%20omniscient%2C%20and%20omnipotent%2C%20we%20ask%20you%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-manipur-narendra-modi-prime-minister%5C%22%3EThe%2