t%20have%20the%20same%20clout%2C%20Gayoom%20has%20remained%20active%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20All%20of%20his%20four%20children%20are%20affiliated%20to%20different%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20PPM.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20Gayoom%E2%80%99s%20MRM%20had%20also%20decided%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20presidential%20elections.%20The%20EC%20had%20earlier%20dissolved%20MRM%20after%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20legal%20requirement%20of%203000%20members.%20MRM%20went%20to%20the%20civil%20court%2C%20which%20ruled%20against%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20move.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.mv%2Fpresidential_election_2023%2F28705%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFaris%20announced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20would%20stand%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%20and%20submitted%20his%20nomination%20just%20before%20the%20deadline.%20With%20at%20least%20one%20member%20of%20his%20family%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20Gayoom%20has%20ensured%20that%20he%20remains%20part%20of%20the%20political%20calculations%20after%20September%209.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691568008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09122311%2FF1OKCIcaIAI3sDv.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-explainer-presidential-election-ibrahim-solih%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Solih%20remains%20the%20frontrunner%2C%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20if%20he%20would%20secure%20an%20outright%20win%20in%20the%20first%20round.%20With%20eight%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20pool%20ever%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20presidential%20election%20in%20Maldive's%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-explainer-presidential-electio