com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-facebook-fabulous-life-career-photos-2017-4%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20not%20have%20gotten%20an%20undergrad%20degree%20out%20of%20Harvard%2C%20but%20he%20has%20his%20time%20at%20the%20university%20to%20thank%20for%20introducing%20him%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpriscilla-chans-childhood-history-2014-5%5C%22%3EPriscilla%20Chan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20met%20in%202003%20at%20a%20frat%20party%2C%20and%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%202012%2C%20one%20day%20after%20the%20IPO%20of%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20as%20Zuckerberg%20has%20continued%20to%20run%20Meta%2C%20the%20couple%20founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-cure-all-disease-explained-2016-9%5C%22%3EChan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pledged%20millions%20to%20philanthropy%20efforts%2C%20started%20a%20family%2C%20and%20traveled%20on%20vacations%20abroad%2C%20all%20while%20buying%20up%20big%20properties%20in%20California%2C%20Lake%20Tahoe%2C%20and%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20couple%2C%20who%20have%20been%20together%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%20and%20have%20three%20daughters%20together%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-censors-daughters-faces-with-emojis-provoking-users-2023-7%5C%22%3EMaxima%2C%20August%2C%20and%20Aurelia%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Chan%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20met%20standing%20in%20line%20for%20the%20bathroom%20at%20a%20Harvard%20University%20party%20in%202003.%20Zuckerberg's%20fraternity%2C%20Alpha%20Epsilon%20Pi%2C%20was%20hosting%20a%20party%20and%20Chan%2C%20a%20sophomore%20student%20from%20the%20Boston%20area%2C%20was%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20this%20nerdy%20guy%20who%20was%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2010%2F09%2F20%2Fthe-face-of-facebook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20he%20had%20these%20beer%20glasses%20that%20said%20'pound%20include%20beer%20dot%20H.'%20It's%20a%20tag%20for%20C%2B%2B.%20It's%20like%20college%20humor%20but%20with%20a%20nerdy%2C%20computer-science%20appeal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20said%20that%20when%20she%20first%20met%20Zuckerberg%2C%20she%20thought%20he%20might%20get%20kicked%20out%20of%20school%20for%20a%20prank%20he%20pulled%3A%20the%20hot-or-not%20website%20ranking%20the%20attractiveness%20of%20students%20on%20campus%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BFacemash%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20Zuckerberg%20notoriously%20created%20in%20his%20sophomore%20year%20at%20Harvard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20also%20expected%20to%20get%20kicked%20out%20of%20Harvard%20when%20he%20met%20Chan.%20The%20party%20was%20a%20farewell%20bash.%20In%20his%202017%20commencement%20address%20at%20Harvard%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-priscilla-chan-met-mark-zuckerberg-2014-5%5C%22%3Eopening%20line%20to%20Chan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20get%20kicked%20out%20in%20three%20days%2C%20so%20we%20need%20to%20go%20on%20a%20date%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20Facemash%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20met%20Priscilla%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20same%20speech.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20the%20most%20important%20person%20in%20my%20life%2C%20so%20you%20could%20say%20it%20was%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20I%20built%20in%20my%20time%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Zuckerberg%20took%20Chan%20out%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20he%20told%20her%20he'd%20%26quot%3Brather%20go%20on%20a%20date%20with%20%5Bher%5D%20than%20finish%20his%20take-home%20midterm%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said