20Asian%20cuisine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20New%20Yorker%20wrote%20about%20the%20couple%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20was%20there%20when%20Zuckerberg%20turned%20down%20multiple%20buyout%20offers%2C%20including%20a%20%241%20billion%20offer%20from%20Yahoo%20in%202006.%20She%20said%20Zuckerberg%20was%20the%20most%20stressed-out%20that%20she'd%20ever%20seen%20him%20during%20that%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20still%20a%20med%20student%20at%20UCSF%2C%20Chan%20moved%20in%20September%202010%20to%20Zuckerberg's%20rented%20house%20in%20the%20College%20Terrace%20neighborhood%20of%20Palo%20Alto.%20He%20announced%20the%20news%20on%20%E2%80%94%20where%20else%20%E2%80%94%20Facebook.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20have%202x%20everything%2C%20so%20if%20you%20need%20any%20household%20appliances%2C%20dishes%2C%20glasses%2C%20etc%20please%20come%20by%20and%20take%20them%20before%20we%20give%20them%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202011%2C%20Chan%20and%20Zuckerberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-industry-titans-dogs-2017-6%5C%22%3Eadopted%20a%20dog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0a%20Puli%20they%20named%20Beast.%20That%20same%20month%2C%20the%20couple%20finally%20made%20their%20relationship%20Facebook%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202011%2C%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Chan%20bought%20a%20five-bedroom%20home%20for%20%247%20million%20in%20Palo%20Alto%20and%20tricked%20it%20out%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bcustom-made%20artificially%20intelligent%20assistant.%26quot%3B%20The%20following%20year%2C%20Zuckerberg%20bought%20the%20four%20homes%20surrounding%20the%20residence%20for%20%2443%20million%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20expand%20his%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-marries-2012-5%5C%22%3EZuckerberg%20and%20Chan's%20wedding%3C%2Fa%3E%20ceremony%20in%20May%202012%20was%20a%20surprise%3A%20The%20couple%20tied%20the%20knot%20just%20days%20after%20Chan%20graduated%20from%20med%