%20said%20that%20the%20opinions%20of%20retired%20judges%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20binding%20diktats%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20refer%20to%20a%20colleague%2C%20you%20have%20to%20refer%20to%20a%20sitting%20colleague.%20Once%20they%20cease%20to%20be%20judges%2C%20they%20are%20opinions%2C%20not%20binding%20diktats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20surprised%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20not%20binding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20said%2C%20in%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Franjan-gogoi-rajya-sabha-first-speech%5C%22%3Emaiden%20Rajya%20Sabha%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20Gogoi%20had%20defended%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%20(which%20is%20now%20an%20Act)%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cperfectly%2C%20legitimately%20valid%E2%80%9D.%20He%20had%20affirmed%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20by%20the%20Centre%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cviolate%20the%20basic%20feature%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20is%20not%20arbitrary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogoi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Monday%20was%20his%20first%20speech%20in%20parliament%20in%20three%20years%20and%20four%20months%20after%20he%20was%20nominated%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Five%20women%20members%20of%20parliament%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20when%20Gogoi%20stood%20to%20talk.%20Gogoi%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20a%20staffer%20while%20she%20was%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fformer-cji-ranjan-gogoi-makes-maiden-speech-in-parliament-in-support-of-delhi-services-bill-2638271%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20making%20Gogoi%20speak%20on%20the%20issue%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20government%20to%20gather%20more%20mass%20in%20the%20perception%20battle%20over%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0which%20has%20been%20panned%20for%20going%20against%20a%20precise%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20and%20impinging%20upon%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20power%20over%20its%20own%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20CJI%20had%20said%20that%20in%20his%20view%20the%20doctrine%20of%20the%20Basic%20Structure%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20has%20a%20very%20%E2%80%9Cdebatable%20jurisprudential%20basis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20objected%20to%20Sibal%E2%80%99s%20reference%20to%20Gogoi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20made%20in%20the%20parliament.%20He%20said%20that%20parliament%20does%20not%20discuss%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20court%20and%20the%20court%20does%20not%20do%20the%20same%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceveryone%20has%20a%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-services-bill-rajya-sabha-arvind-kejriwal-centre-ias-officer-amit-shah%5C%22%3Epassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20with%20131%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20it%2C%20and%20102%20against%20it.%20The%20Bill%20was%20earlier%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-passes-delhi-services-bill-amit-shah-attacks-aap-accuses-india-of-uniting-only-for-polls%5C%22%3Epassed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Elast%20week%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691564723000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F26154637%2Faa-Cover-ss7kpl0727ljnfcnj2u2t6u5k7-20180926134405.Medi_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fopinions-not-diktats-cji-chandrachud-on-ranjan-gogois-remarks-on-constitutions-basic-structure%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20CJI%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%