t%3B%20PM%20Modi%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%2082%2C%20exited%20the%20Congress%20in%201999%20following%20his%20revolt%20over%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20foreign%20origin.%20Days%20later%2C%20he%20formed%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20which%20recently%20split%20after%20a%20coup%20by%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20made%20the%20comments%20as%20NCP%20fights%20off%20rumours%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20is%20warming%20up%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20veteran%20himself%20reportedly%20assured%20his%20party%20workers%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20would%20not%20join%20forces%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20yesterday's%20meeting%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20attacked%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20suffered%20a%20similar%20split%20last%20year%20and%20lost%20power%20after%20rebel%20Eknath%20Shinde%20walked%20out%20and%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20break%20the%20alliance%20with%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20they%20did.%20Since%202014%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%2C%20but%20their%20party's%20newspaper%20'Saamana'%20constantly%20criticized%20our%20government.%20Unfounded%20criticism%20was%20published%20and%20controversies%20were%20stirred%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20tolerated%20this.%20We%20took%20it%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20power%20together%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20also%20criticize.%20How%20can%20both%20things%20happen%20together%3F%20Eknath%20Shinde%20joined%20us%2C%20and%20he%20was%20given%20the%20position%20of%20Chief%20Minister.%20We%20will%20stay%20together%3B%20there%20will%20be%20respect%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20saying%20parties%20who%20want%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20%26quot%3Bare%20welcome%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C