22author%22%3A%22JASPREET%20SAHNI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fhockey%2Ftop-stories%2Fasian-champions-trophy-when-its-india-vs-pakistan-coaching-takes-backseat-says-rehan-butt%2Farticleshow%2F102562381.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Dozens'%20of%20migrants%20killed%20in%20shipwreck%20off%20Italian%20coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691562120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-lampedusa-italy-boats_6245132.jpg%3F20230809094901%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdozens-of-migrants-killed-in-shipwreck-off-italian-coast-12936465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forty-one%20migrants%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20a%20shipwreck%20off%20the%20island%20of%20Lampedusa%20in%20Italy%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdozens-of-migrants-killed-in-shipwreck-off-italian-coast-12936465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdozens-of-migrants-killed-in-shipwreck-off-italian-coast-12936465%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdozens-of-migrants-killed-in-shipwreck-off-italian-coast-12936465%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20To%20Look%20Into%20'Havana%20Syndrome'%3A%20All%20About%20The%20Mysterious%20Illness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20told%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20will%20look%20into%20the%20'Havana%20Syndrome'%20issue%20in%20India.%20The%20response%20was%20filed%20on%20a%20petition%20of%20Bengaluru%20resident%20A%20Amarnath%20Chagu%2C%20who%20sought%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20mysterious%20illness%20in%20India%20and%20directions%20to%20the%20central%20government%20to%20prevent%20its%20transmission%20within%20India.%20In%20its%20July%2027%20order%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20the%20Centre's%20counsel%20agreed%20to%20examine%20the%20matter%20and%20said%20the%20time%20for%20consideration%20is%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20then%20disposed%20of%20the%20writ%20petition.%20The%20petitioner's%20lawyer%20Srikanth%20VK%20had%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20are%20bound%20to%20consider%20the%20issue%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%20since%20that%20is%20the%20mandate%20under%20Article%20350%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20350%2C%20every%20person%20shall%20be%20entitled%20to%20submit%20a%20representation%20for%20the%20redress%20of%20any%20grievance%20to%20any%20officer%20or%20authority%20of%20the%20Union%20or%20State%20in%20any%20of%20the%20languages%20used%20in%20the%20Union%20or%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Havana%20syndrome%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mysterious%20illness%20was%20first%20reported%20in%202016%20when%20CIA%20employees%20stationed%20in%20Cuba's%20Havana%20reported%20experiencing%20unusual%20symptoms%20such%20as%20migraines%2C%20nausea%2C%20memory%20lapses%2C%20dizziness%2C%20hearing%20sounds%20without%20any%20external%20noise%2C%20and%20vertigo.%20Some%20of%20these%20officials%20claimed%20that%20the%20symptoms%20lasted%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20name%20has%20been%20given%2C%20the%20exact%20cause%20of%20the%20syndrome%20remains%20elusive%2C%20with%20possible%20links%20to%20high-frequency%20microwave%20emissions%20-%20something%20that%20the%20petitioner%20highlighted%20in%20his%20plea%20before%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReported%20cases%20of%20Havana%20syndrome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20US%20intelligence%20and%20embassy%20officials%20are%20said%20to%20have%20experienced%20mental%20health%20symptoms%20attributed%20to%20Havana%20syndrome%20in%20various%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202018%2C%20MRI%20scams%20and%20other%20tests%20taken%20by%20a%20neurologist%20in%20Pittsburgh%20on%20some%20Canadian%20diplomats%20showed%20signs%20of%20brain%20damage%20that%20their%20US%20counterparts%20claimed%20to%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20similar%20reports%20about%20US%20intelligence%20officials%20experiencing%20unexplained%20symptoms%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Tbilisi%2C%20Poland%2C%20Taiwan%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20US%20responded%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20CIA%20issued%20an%20interim%20assessment%20concluding%20that%20the%20syndrome%20is%20not%20the%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20sustained%20global%20campaign%20by%20a%20hostile%20power%26quot%3B.%20Foreign%20involvement%20was%20ruled%20out%20in%20976%20cases%20of%20the%201%2C000%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20US%20passed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F117th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1828%5C%22%3Enew%20law%20titled%20HAVANA%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Helping%20American%20Victims%20Afflicted%20by%20Neurological%20Attacks%20Act)%20to%20authorise%20the%20provision%20of%20payment%20to%20intelligence%20personnel%20and%20diplomats%20who%20incurred%20injuries%2C%20and%20for%20other%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691561940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fsl8ou6v_us-embassy-in-havana_625x300_23_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcentre-agrees-to-look-into-havana-syndrome-in-india-all-about-the-mysterious-illness-4282114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Havana%20syndrome%20is%20a%20mysterious%20illness%20experienced%20by%20US%20intelligence%20officials%20and%20diplomats%20with%20symptoms%20like%20migraines%2C%20nausea%20and%20memory%20lapses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com