ades%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22acpqmu88%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Facpqmu88_arvind-kejriwal-thank-you-note-to-rahul-gandhi_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20write%20to%20you%20expressing%20gratitude%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20two%20crore%20people%20of%20Delhi%20for%20your%20party's%20support%20in%20rejecting%20and%20voting%20against%20the%20GNCTD%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20place%20on%20record%20the%20heartfelt%20appreciation%20for%20championing%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20inside%20as%20well%20as%20outside%20the%20Parliament.%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20your%20unflinching%20loyalty%20towards%20the%20principles%20of%20our%20Constitution%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20decades.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20your%20continued%20support%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20forces%20that%20are%20undermining%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20Central%20government%20control%20over%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20cleared%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20and%20will%20become%20law%20after%20the%20President's%20signoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20was%20able%20to%20get%20the%20bill%20through%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%2C%20as%20parties%20like%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20had%20rallied%20opposition%20parties%20nationwide%20in%20AAP's%20fight%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20had%20sought%20the%20Congress's%20support%20despite%20the%20intense%20rivalry%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20states%20like%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress's%20vacillation%20threatened%20to%20derail%20opposition%20unity%20meetings%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20come%20o