20a%20written%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Finance%20Pankaj%20Chaudhary%20gave%20details%20of%20the%20income%20tax%20paid%20by%20the%20BCCI%20and%20its%20income%20and%20expenditures%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20based%20on%20the%20returns%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earning%20from%20the%20ICC%20revenue%20pool%20is%20only%20one%20of%20the%20sources%20for%20the%20BCCI.%20The%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20remains%20another%20big-money%20tournament%20for%20the%20Indian%20board%20that%20fetches%20them%20huge%20money.%20The%20IPL%20remains%20the%20most%20lucrative%20league%20in%20the%20world%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20players'%20participation%20and%20sponsorships.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20only%20expected%20to%20strengthen%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20financial%20year%202020-21%2C%20BCCI%20paid%20Rs%20844.92%20crore%20in%20income%20tax%2C%20slightly%20lower%20than%20Rs%20882.29%20crore%20paid%20in%202019-20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20FY2019%2C%20the%20board%20paid%20Rs%20815.08%20crore%20as%20taxes%2C%20higher%20than%20Rs%20596.63%20crore%20paid%20in%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021-22%20fiscal%2C%20BCCI%20had%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%207%2C606%20crore%2C%20while%20its%20expenditure%20stood%20at%20close%20to%20Rs%203%2C064%20crore.%20In%202020-21%2C%20its%20income%20stood%20at%20Rs%204%2C735%20crore%20and%20expenditure%20at%20Rs%203%2C080%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691558220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F5gn8prd_jay-shah-650_650x400_19_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhow-much-tax