normous%20capacity%20to%20force%20you%20to%20think%20about%20the%20rural%20oppression%20of%20peasants%20and%20the%20tribal%20communities%C2%A0%20is%20an%20understatement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaddar%20mesmerised%20everyone%20with%20his%20group%20of%20three%20to%20four%20singers.%20For%20my%20brother%2C%20Gaddar%E2%80%99s%20famous%20song%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnm5O2wkCxzY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERela%20Re%2C%20Rela%20Re%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20morning%20ritual.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20not%20a%20moment%20when%20my%2078-year-old%20brother%20would%20not%20sing%20this%20particular%20song%20of%20Gaddar.%20It%20is%20a%20folk%20song%20that%20explains%20the%20daily%20existence%2C%20struggles%20and%20world%20view%20of%20tribal%20communities%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20song%20is%20a%20gem%20in%20itself.%20A%20moving%20song%20about%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20%E2%80%98Oh%20Police%20Anna%E2%80%99%20describes%20how%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20your%20life%2C%20their%20daily%20plight%20and%20our%20struggles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPNmDvOr1t0I%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20song%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgAipX6WfJyo%5C%22%3ENindu%20Amasanadu%20Oh%20Laccha%20Gummadi%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20explains%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20girl%2C%20how%20valuable%20it%20is%20and%20how%20she%20carries%20her%20daily%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRvgjQYsfAII%