gularly%2C%20so%20even%20if%20you%20block%20its%20bot%20now%2C%20your%20data%20has%20already%20probably%20been%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20unaware%20of%20anyone%20that%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20Common%20Crawl%20to%20remove%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Clarke%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20tried%2C%20but%20have%20had%20no%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Opt-in'%20not%20'opt-out'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClarke%20and%20others%20are%20now%20calling%20for%20these%20AI%20spiderbots%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bopt-in%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Bopt-out.%26quot%3B%20Right%20now%2C%20OpenAI%20scrapes%20everyone's%20data%20as%20the%20default%2C%20and%20creators%20must%20take%20steps%20to%20opt%20out%20and%20actively%20block%20it.%20An%20%26quot%3Bopt-in%26quot%3B%20approach%20would%20require%20OpenAI%20to%20ask%20permission%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20collection%20methods%20for%20these%20models%20must%20become%20strictly%20opt-in.%20Many%20people%20will%20not%20find%20out%20how%20to%20protect%20their%20work%20until%20it%20has%20already%20been%20taken%2C%20yet%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Clarke%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSince%20we%20are%20presently%20unable%20to%20have%20our%20content%20removed%20from%20existing%20models%20and%20scraped%20data%20sets%2C%20opt-out%20is%20not%20enough.%20It%20is%20not%20our%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20data%20for%20these%20companies%2C%20nor%20should%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20simply%20take%20it%20without%20consent%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20benefits%20they%20imagine%20coming%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20OpenAI%20about%20all%20this%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%20The%20company%20didn't%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPaying%20for%20AI%20training%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20respect%20some%20online%20data.%20GPTbot%20is%20now%20designed%20to%20filter%20out%20sources%20that%20require%20paywall%20access%20and%20to%20remove%20other%20sources%20known%20to%20gather%20personally%2