e%20demanding%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20house%20to%20address%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20even%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20remained%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20continued%20for%20six%20hours%2C%20with%20speeches%20from%2018%20MPs%2C%20including%20two%20Union%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20focused%20on%20the%20ongoing%20spiralling%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20%E2%80%93%20the%20treasury%20benches%20attacked%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20highlighted%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2026%2C%20the%20Congress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-congress-no-confidence-modi-speaker%5C%22%3Emoved%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Opposition%20members%20said%20that%20the%20move%20is%20crucial%20for%20Modi%20to%20speak%20in%20parliament%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203.%20Over%20150%20people%20have%20died%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3EModi%20did%20speak%20last%20month%20outside%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20condemning%20a%20video%20that%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Eviral%20showing%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20overall%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%202018%2C%20this%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistory-no-confidence-motions-modi-government%5C%22%3Esecond%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98If%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20then%20India%20is%20burning%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20was%20opened%20by%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20house%2C%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20had%20moved%20the%20motion%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20party%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fno-confidence-motion-rahul-gandhi-likely-to-open-debate-from-opposition-side%2F1704941%2F%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20newly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-days-after-sc-stays-defamation-conviction-lok-sabha-reinstates-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3Ereinstated%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20open%20the%20debate%2C%20it%20was%20Gogoi%20who%20started%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogoi%20said%20that%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20has%20been%20brought%20because%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20taken%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaun%20vrat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vow%20of%20silence).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-manipur-gujarat%5C%22%3EIt%20Is%20Na%C3%AFve%20to%20Expect%20PM%20Modi%20to%20Speak%20up%20During%20Crises%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20bring%20this%20no%20confidence%20motion.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20numbers%2C%20but%20of%20justice.%20Manipur%20wants%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMartin%20Luther%20King%20has%20said%20that%20injustice%20anywhere%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20justice%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20if%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20then%20India%20is%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20demand%20was%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20PM%20should%20come%20to%20the%20house%20and%20speak%2C%20so%20that%20Manipur%20gets%20the%20message%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20wants%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20this%20did%20not%20happen.%20The%20PM%20has%20taken%20a%20maun%20vrat%20that%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20speak%20either%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20why%20we%20had%20to%20bring%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosing%20three%20questions%20to%20Modi%2C%20Gogoi%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20to%20answer%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20he%20%5BModi%5D%20been%20to%20Manipur%20yet%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRahul%20Gandhi%20went%2C%20INDIA%20alliance%20went%2C%20home%20minister%20went%2C%20MoS%20home%20went%20but%20Modi%20did%20not%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FBiren-Singh_PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22267%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-125344%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20CM%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20it%20take%20around%2080%20days%20for%20the%20PM%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%2C%20that%20too%20for%2030%20seconds%3F%20Even%20now%20there%20has%20been%20no%20message%20of%20peace%20from%20Modi.%20Ministers%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20we%20will%20speak%20on%20Manipur.%20Please%20do%20%E2%80%93%20no%20one%20has%20stopped%20you.%20But%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20his%20words%20carry%20more%20weight%20than%20any%20minister.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogoi%20added%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20changed%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Tripura%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20head%20of%20state%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhose%20blessings%20does%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20have%20that%20he%20is%20not%20being%20removed%3F%20Modi%20has%20to%20admit%20that%20his%20double-engine%20government%20has%20failed%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Nine%20governments%20toppled%20in%20nine%20years%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Opposition%20MPs%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20why%20Modi%20was%20not%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20has%20elected%20him%20to%20attend%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20MP%20T.R.%20Balu.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20he%20not%20attending%20parliament%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Sougata%20Roy%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20nothing%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20against%20Modi%E2%80%9D%2C%20anyone%20who%20loves%20India%20cannot%20love%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20that%20I%20love%20Modi%20less%2C%20but%20%5Bthat%5D%20I%20love%20India%20more.%20If%20anyone%20loves%20India%2C%20they%20will%20not%20love%20Modi.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20make%20it%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20is%20sending%20delegations%20to%20West%20Bengal%20on%20everything%2C%20but%20not%20one%20delegation%20has%20gone%20to%20Manipur%20where%20our%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20are%20dying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20PM%20has%20to%20reply%20why%20he%20was%20visiting%20foreign%20countries%20when%20Manipur%20was%20burning.%20The%20PM%20has%20failed%20to%20check%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20failed%20to%20provide%20jobs%20and%20protect%20social%20harmony.%20We%20are%20seeing%20the%20communal%20riots%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana.%20Only%20Muslim%20houses%20are%20being%20destroyed.%20Modi%20never%20comes%20to%20parliament.%20He%20has%20not%20replied%20to%20a%20single%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20price%20rise%2C%20inflation%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20demonetisation%20and%20the%20sudden%20lockdown%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20that%20forced%20migrant%20workers%20to%20walk%20back%20to%20their%20villages%2C%20Roy%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20compassion%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20visible%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20has%20not%20given%20a%20response%20on%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%20PM%20avoids%20all%20discussion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fgautam-adani%5C%22%3EAdani%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20achievement%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20in%20toppling%20governments%20in%20Opposition-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNine%20governments%20have%20been%20toppled%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20demand%20that%20the%20CM%20must%20resign.%20How%20can%20we%20allow%20this%3F%2010%2C000%20cases%20of%20rioting%2C%20murder%2C%20rape.%20Have%20we%20become%20so%20insensitive%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-india-bloc-derek-obrien-karan-thapar%5C%22%3EFrom%20Potential%20Discord%20to%20PM%20Face%2C%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20Addresses%20Key%20Questions%20on%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDimple%20Yadav%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20to%20bring%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20the%20house%2C%20he%20was%20still%20not%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20BJP%20leaders%E2%80%99%20charge%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Opposition-ruled%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20when%20asked%20about%20Manipur%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20should%20talk%20about%20other%20states.%20Every%20three%20hours%2C%20one%20woman%20is%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20UP%20and%20the%20double-engine%20government%20%5Bof%20the%20BJP%5D%20is%20not%20taking%20note%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20situation.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20has%20been%20concerning.%20There%20has%20been%20complete%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20using%20women%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20perpetuating%20violence%20is%20simply%20unacceptable%20in%20%5Ba%5D%20constitutional%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloves%20off%20over%20%E2%80%98INDIA%E2%80%99%20alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20centred%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98INDIA%E2%80%99%20for%20its%20alliance%20of%2026%20parties%20that%20have%20joined%20hands%20to%20fight%20Modi%20unitedly%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20kicked%20off%20the%20debate%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20accused%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20independent%20journalists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3Eof%20having%20links%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20reports%20in%20the%20media%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20speak.%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20he%20is%20not%20ready%2C%20maybe%20he%20woke%20up%20late%20so%20he%20is%20not%20speaking%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stay%20on%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%2C%20Dubey%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20MP%20has%20refused%20to%20apologise%20because%20Modi%20is%20the%20name%20of%20a%20lower%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20ask%20for%20forgiveness%20or%20apologise%20because%20Modi%20is%20a%20lower%20caste%20and%20Rahul%20is%20a%20big%20man.%20He%20says%20he%20is%20not%20Savarkar.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20he%20can%20never%20be%20Savarkar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08233020%2FNishikant-Dubey.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08233020%2FNishikant-Dubey.jpg%20915w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08233020%2FNishikant-Dubey-300x157.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667244%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPictured%20here%20speaking%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20had%20earlier%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20receiving%20funds%20from%20China.%20Photo%3A%20Screenshot%20from%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20aim%20at%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20house%2C%20Dubey%20said%20that%20she%20was%20acting%20like%20any%20Indian%20woman.%20%E2%80%9CBete%20ko%20set%20karna%20hai%2C%20damaad%20ko%20bhent%20karna%20hai%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98she%20has%20to%20set%20up%20her%20son%2C%20and%20gift%20her%20son-in-law%E2%80%99%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%20said%20that%20several%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20may%20not%20even%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20the%20full%20form%20of%20the%20acronym.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20says%20this%20is%20not%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20but%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20on%20the%20Opposition%20and%20about%20who%20is%20with%20whom%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cson%20of%20a%20poor%20man%2C%20against%20a%20man%20who%20gave%20people%20houses%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20toilets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrikant%20Shinde%2C%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%2C%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20said%20that%20they%20changed%20their%20name%20from%20UPA%20to%20INDIA%20because%20the%20word%20UPA%20is%20only%20reminiscent%20of%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20already%20given%20no-confidence%20against%20you%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20and%20%5Ba%5D%20hat-trick%20will%20come%20in%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20changed%20their%20name%20from%20UPA%20to%20INDIA%20%E2%80%93%20they%20think%20by%20this%2C%20people%20of%20the%20country%20will%20be%20with%20them.%20But%20the%20reason%20they%20changed%20their%20name%20is%20because%20they%20are%20ashamed%20of%20%5Bthe%20name%5D%20%E2%80%98UPA%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20reminds%20people%20of%20scams.%20Between%202004-14%2C%20India%20only%20got%20scams%20and%20corruption%20and%20countless%20terror%20attacks.%20Today%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20they%20will%20lecture%20people%20on%20democracy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20every%20politician%20is%20a%20PM-in-waiting.%20This%20team%20has%20no%20captain%20but%20they%20want%20to%20win%20the%20match.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fight%20of%20scheme%20versus%20scam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frestoration-of-rahul-gandhis-lok-sabha-members-is-a-rebuke-to-narendra-modi%5C%22%3ERestoration%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20Membership%20Is%20a%20Rebuke%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20also%20saw%20a%20heated%20war%20of%20words%20between%20the%20warring%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20over%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Arvind%20Sawant%20(Shiv%20Sena%20Uddhav%20faction%20MP)%20who%20said%20that%20Hindutva%20does%20not%20include%20%E2%80%9Ccowards%E2%80%9D%2C%20Union%20minister%20Narayan%20Tatu%20Rane%20said%20that%20if%20the%20party%20had%20such%20high%20regard%20for%20Hindutva%2C%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20align%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20love%20Hindutva%20so%20much%2C%20why%20did%20they%20betray%20Hindutva%20and%20go%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%202019%3F%20They%20are%20talking%20about%20Hindutva%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERane%20has%20been%20part%20of%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Duggal%2C%20BJP%20MP%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20can%20adopt%20any%20name%20but%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20win%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20make%20any%20alliance%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20INDIA%20or%20ghamandiyaa%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98greedy%E2%80%99%5D%20%E2%80%93%20they%20cannot%20win%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20people.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20bhavishyavaani%20%5Bprediction%5D%20will%20succeed%20and%20the%20BJP%20will%20form%20the%20government%20in%202024.%20And%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20bring%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20in%20parliament%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20that%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20had%20brought%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20wrong%20time%20and%20in%20the%20wrong%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20tell%20on%20record%20that%20the%20Opposition%20will%20regret%20this%20no%20confidence%20motion%20which%20has%20been%20brought%20at%20the%20wrong%20time%20and%20in%20the%20wrong%20manner.%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20image%20is%20only%20getting%20better%20and%20Modi%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20global%20leader%2C%20and%20many%20believe%20that%20he%20can%20lead%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorld%20leaders%20come%20to%20India%20and%20want%20to%20work%20with%20India%2C%20G20%20meetings%20are%20underway%20in%20many%20states.%20Under%20such%20circumstances%2C%20instead%20of%20standing%20with%20the%20government%2C%20they%20have%20brought%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20why%20I%20say%20they%20will%20suffer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20Modi%20or%20BJP%2C%20if%20India%20is%20moving%20forward%2C%20you%20should%20support%20us.%20You%20cannot%20oppose%20us%20and%20name%20yourselves%20INDIA.%20The%20country%20will%20not%20fall%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERijiju%20also%20said%20that%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20Northeastern%20states%20have%20been%20highlighted%2C%20connectivity%20has%20been%20improved%20and%20coverage%20under%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20has%20been%20reduced%20by%2075%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20of%20not%20meeting%20leaders%20and%20MPs%20from%20the%20Northeast%2C%20Rijiju%20said%20that%20Modi%20had%20instructed%20a%20group%20of%20ministers%20to%20visit%20th%20Northeastern%20states%20every%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20the%20government%20should%20furnish%20details%20of%20such%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20all%20know%20about%20the%20frequency%20of%20visits%20of%20Union%20Ministers%20before%20any%20election.%20But%20it%20has%20been%2097%20days%20since%20the%20horrific%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur.%20INDIA%20asks%20how%20many%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ministers%20have%20been%20to%20Manipur%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20No%20Confidence%20Motion%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20has%20boasted%20about%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20directions%20to%20Cabinet%20Ministers%20and%20Ministers%20of%20State%20to%20visit%20Northeast%20every%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20all%20know%20about%20the%20frequency%20of%20visits%20of%20Union%20Ministers%20before%20any%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1688867868358619136%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20challenge%20you%20to%20furnish%20details%20of%20the%20visits%20of%20Union%20ministers%20to%20Manipur%20in%20the%20last%2097%20days!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20from%20BJD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20found%20support%20from%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%2C%20whose%20MP%20Pinaki%20Misra%20said%20that%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20defies%20%E2%80%9Ccommon%20sense%2C%20political%20sense%20and%20logic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNaveen%20Patnaik%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20needlessly%20picking%20fights%20with%20the%20central%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20justifying%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20stand%20to%20support%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20reason%20why%20this%20motion%20has%20been%20brought%20is%20to%20bring%20the%20PM%20to%20the%20house.%20But%20every%20time%20he%20is%20in%20the%20house%2C%20he%20puts%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20shredder.%20Why%20do%20they%20want%20him%20to%20do%20that%3F%20This%20defies%20common%20sense%2C%20logic%20and%20political%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20this%20country%20will%20decide%20whether%20it%20is%20right%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20spoken%20in%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20the%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9C50-60%20years%20of%20strife.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-naveen-patnaik-path-keep-your-friends-close-but-the-bjp-closer%5C%22%3EThe%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20Path%3A%20Keep%20Your%20Friends%20Close%2C%20But%20the%20BJP%20Closer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERow%20over%20Sansad%20TV%20ticker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20debate%20also%20saw%20a%20row%20between%20the%20Opposition%20and%20treasury%20benches%20over%20ticker%20lines%20being%20run%20on%20Sansad%20TV%20that%20showed%20the%20government%20ministries%E2%80%99%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20members%20interrupted%20BJP%20MP%20Dubey%2C%20who%20had%20just%20begun%20his%20speech%2C%20and%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20ticker%20during%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20controls%20over%20what%20is%20being%20run.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMere%20paas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebutton%3Cem%3E%20nahi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20(Hindi%20for%20%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20button%E2%80%99)%20Birla%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Birla%20said%20that%20he%20will%20look%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%20Lok%20Sabha%20TV%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20TV%20have%20merged%20into%20Sansad%20TV.%20You%20have%20brought%20this%20matter%20to%20my%20notice%20and%20the%20team%20is%20looking%20into%20it.%20It%20will%20be%20stopped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20such%20a%20ticker%20always%20runs%20during%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20speech%20is%20telecast%20live.%20Why%20are%20they%20so%20scared%3F%20The%20Opposition%20should%20not%20be%20so%20insecure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20day%20of%20the%20debate%20also%20included%20speeches%20from%20Communist%20Pary%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20MP%20A.M.%20Arif%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%20MP%20N.K.%20Premachandran%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20and%20independent%20MP%20Navneet%20Rana%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20on%20Wednesday%20(August%209)%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reply%20is%20expected%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691518740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08234027%2FGaurav-Gogoi-in-LS.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20debate%20continued%20for%20six%20hours%20and%20featured%20speeches%20from%2018%20MPs%2C%20including%20two%20Union%20ministers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan%20barred%20from%20politics%20for%20five%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691515952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12641%2Fproduction%2F_130692357_eecc701a144f9cd38b8fbaa9f5e6dd27565e28680_0_5500_30931000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworl