%20in%20the%20U.K%E2%80%A6%20But%20within%20a%20constitution%20like%20ours%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20a%20referendum%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Farticle-370-hearing-india-seeks-public-opinion-through-established-institutions-not-brexit-type-referendums-says-cji%2Farticle67172076.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%20had%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20reading%20down%20the%20Article%20%E2%80%9Cunilaterally%E2%80%9D%20without%20making%20an%20effort%20to%20understand%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20want%20to%20sever%20such%20a%20special%20relationship%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20you%20had%20to%20ultimately%20seek%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20will%20of%20the%20people%20was%20central%20to%20this%20decision.%20It%20should%20have%20been%20a%20political%20decision%E2%80%A6%20What%20happened%20in%20Brexit%3F%20There%20was%20no%20constitutional%20provision%20for%20a%20referendum.%20Yet%2C%20they%20asked%20for%20public%20opinion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20had%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Article%20was%20abrogated%20through%20a%20series%20of%20%E2%80%9Cexecutive%20acts%E2%80%9D%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Legislative%20Assembly%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20was%20imposed%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20and%20a%20proviso%20to%20Article%20370%20(3)%20was%20tweaked%20to%20%E2%80%9Csidestep%20the%20pre-condition%20of%20getting%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20now%20defunct%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Constituent%20Assembly%20before%20declaring%20Article%20370%20inoperative%E2%80%9D%2C%20t