0IST%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20ISRO%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChandrayaan%20has%20many%20critical%20events%20lined%20up%2C%20including%20earth-bound%20manoeuvres%2C%20insertion%20into%20the%20lunar%20orbit%2C%20separation%20of%20the%20lander%2C%20a%20set%20of%20deboost%20manoeuvres%20and%20a%20power%20descent%20phase%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20project%20director%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20spacecraft%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20orbit-raising%20maneuver%20(Earth-bound%20perigee%20firing)%20is%20performed%20successfully%20from%20ISTRAC%2FISRO%2C%20Bengaluru.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20spacecraft%20is%20expected%20to%20attain%20an%20orbit%20of%20127609%20km%20x%20236%20km.%20The%20achieved%20orbit%20will%20be%20confirmed%20after%20the%20observations.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLYb4XBMaU3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLYb4XBMaU3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1683767962560512000%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20will%20go%20around%20the%20Moon%20to%20reduce%20its%20velocity%20in%20orbit%20and%20prepare%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20its%20surface.%20This%20orbiting%20will%20continue%20till%20Chandrayaan-3%20reaches%20a%20circular%20orbit%20of%20100%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20is%20achieved%2C%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20will%20descend%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F216483%2Fiisc-isro-moon-lunar-soi