!%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rahul%20Singh%2C%20co-founder%20of%20EcoSoul%20Home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20laughs%20and%20shares%20the%20reality%20of%20startups%2C%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20glitzy%20world%20many%20might%20imagine%20it%20to%20be.%20But%20this%20was%20the%20foundation%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325587%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-runs-lending-platform-for-rural-indian-women-loans-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20current%20company%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%20now%20poised%20to%20reach%20a%20%2450%20million%20revenue%20run%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Singh%20and%20his%20co-founder%20Arvind%20Ganesan%20quit%20their%20high-flying%20corporate%20jobs%20to%20build%20EcoSoul%20Home%20%E2%80%94%20a%20startup%20which%20sells%20eco-friendly%20home%20essentials%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20replace%20their%20plastic%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERiding%20the%20sustainability%20wave%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201279px)%20100vw%2C%201279px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ecosoul%20bowl%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035.jpeg%201279w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-768x961.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-1228x1536.jpeg%201228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F