terindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-1690551451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-1690551451-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-1690551451-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarun%20has%20installed%20over%203%2C500%20solar%20dryers%20in%20the%20rural%20and%20remote%20farms%20of%20the%20country%20including%20Kashmir%2C%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Arunachal.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20help%20them%20process%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311423%2Futtarakhand-nidhi-pant-agritech-startup-support-women-farmers-helps-them-earn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcess%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20tribal%20remote%20areas%20and%20get%20a%20better%20income.%20We%20have%20been%20able%20to%20boost%20farm%20income%20by%2050%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncreasing%20shelf%20life%20by%20a%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20a%20self-sustainable%20model%2C%20the%20solar%20dryers%20do%20not%20require%20power%20or%20maintenance.%20In%20the%20water-proof%20dryers%2C%20slices%20of%20vegetables%20are%20placed%20and%20within%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20the%20produce%20is%20sun-dried%20and%20ready%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20value-added%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20sun-dried%20tomatoes%20are%20used%20to%20prepare%20oats%20and%20soups%20as%20well%20as%20pizza%20toppings.%20Raw%20bananas%20are%20converted%20into%20banana%20chips%2C%20grapes%20into%20raisins%2C%20and%20onions%20into%20onion%20flakes.%20Varun%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20vegetable%20and%20fruit%2C%20even%20a%20watermelon%2C%20can%20be%20dried%20into%20a%20value-added%20product.%20There%20is%20an%20unlimited%20scope%20and%20demand%20for%20such%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20dryer%20dehydrates%20moisture%20of%20the%20fresh%20produce%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20retains%20the%20taste%2C%20colour%2C%20aroma%2C%20and%20nutrients%20of%20the%20product%2C%20he%20says.%20Not%20only%20this%20but%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20perishable%20food%20products%20is%20also%20increased%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%20one%20year%20or%20more%20without%20using%20any%20additives%20or%20preservatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20and%20his%20team%20help%20farmers%20install%20solar%20dryers%20at%20remotest%20locations.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-2-1690551674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325725%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarun%20and%20his%20team%20help%20farmers%20install%20solar%20dryers%20at%20remotest%20locations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarun%20has%20partnered%20with%20at%20least%20170%20organisations%20like%20Sahaydri%20Farms%2C%20PRADAN%2C%20and%20TATA%20Trust%20to%20engage%20with%20farmers%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20After%20installing%20solar%20dryers%2C%20his%20team%20trains%20them%20to%20convert%20the%20produce%20into%20dried%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20also%20supports%20farmers%20in%20the%20marketing%20of%20their%20dried%20products%20by%20selling%20them%20to%20their%20network%20of%20200%20FMCG%20companies%20in%20India.%20At%20the%20decentralised%20collection%20centres%20established%20in%20almost%20every%20state%2C%20the%20dried%20products%20are%20collected.%20After%20quality%20checks%20and%20sorting%20based%20on%20colour%20and%20size%2C%20the%20products%20are%20sterilised%20and%20packaged%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20FMCG%20brands%20like%20Happilo%20and%20Chaayos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20just%20selling%20solar%20dryers%2C%20we%20are%20building%20an%20ecosystem%20where%20farmers%20learn%20how%20to%20practise%20this%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun%2C%20who%20aims%20to%20onboard%20three%20lakh%20farmers%20by%20the%20year-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20I%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20even%20reach%20this%20level.%20It%20is%20unbelievable%20most%20of%20the%20time%20that%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20remotest%20locations%20across%20the%20country.%20Currently%2C%20I%20am%20working%20on%20a%20model%20in%20which%20I%20am%20able%20to%20utilise%20papaya%20peels%20and%20seeds%20in%20the%20cosmetic%20industry.%20And%20thereby%20help%20farmers%20double%20their%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Raheja%20Solar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFood%20Processing%20Pvt%20Ltd%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690811899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325711%22%2